creator: Enel X s.r.l.
descriptionHtml:
Enel X JuicePass is the best way to charge your electric vehicle. Use the app to charge at public charging stations covered by the Enel X Network and at home with your private wallbox.

Want to join the service? After downloading the app and signing up, just activate a profile, select a fee plan and enter a payment method. You’ll be ready to start!

For public charging, the Enel X JuicePass app allows you to: 
• See and locate on the map all the compatible charging stations
• Reserve a plug for 15 minutes and look at the fastest route to reach it
• Start and stop charging sessions
• Purchase the Enel X JuicePass card
• Monitor the supplied energy and charging power in real time
• Pay for your sessions through the app
• Be notified when new charging stations are installed in your area
• Receive live notifications related to an active charging session
• Monitor your consumption and previous charging sessions
• Access the closest available charging station through the widget

For private charging, the app allows you to: 
• Pair your private wallbox to your Enel X JuicePass account
• Start and stop charging sessions and monitor them
• Schedule a charging session and set a preferred duration

Download the app to begin your journey in the electric vehicles world!

Like us on Facebook at https://www.facebook.com/enelxitalia

title: JuicePass

creator: Enel X SRL
descriptionHtml:
Charging your electric car is made easy with JuicePass.
JuicePass is Enel X Way's mobile app that allows you to manage all your electric or plug-in hybrid car charging needs wherever you are.
With access to over 200,000 charging points in Italy and Europe, you can find, or filter nearby charging stations based on availability, max charging power or plug type with the built-in interactive live map.
Charge your EV with JuicePass!
Access public charging networks or manage your Enel X Way JuiceBox home charger.
Download the app for free and register in just a few clicks.
With intuitive navigation and features, JuicePass is an app that makes charging your EV easier.
Enel X Way's mobile app works on all smartphone devices and in all countries allowing you to find the closest charging station when you travel.
JuicePass is convenient
With a few clicks JuicePass allows you to find where you can charge your EV, choose the rate plans that best suit your needs and customize your charging experience by entering your car make model.
JuicePass is multifunctional
Pick the charging station that works for your electric or hybrid car, find charging cost or availability hours and even reserve the charging station in advance.
Check your charging history, energy consumption, past invoices and more.
With JuicePass you can manage your home charging.
Configure and manage a JuiceBox home charger for a complete charging experience.
JuicePass allows you to:
Configure one or more JuiceBox chargers directly from the mobile app
Start or stop charging sessions or monitor charging progress.
Use smart charging features, postpone or delay charging start time and set its duration
Share your JuiceBox with other users
Download the app and start your journey into the world of electric mobility!
Follow us on Facebook at: https://www.facebook.com/enelxway
Need help? Write us at enelxway.italy.support@enel.com

JuicePass is Enel X Way's mobile app that allows you to manage all your electric or plug-in hybrid car charging needs wherever you are.
With access to over 245.000 charging points in Italy and Europe, you can find, or filter nearby charging stations based on availability, max charging power or plug type with the built-in interactive live map.
Charge your EV with JuicePass!
Access public charging networks or manage your Enel X Way JuiceBox home charger.
Download the app for free and register in just a few clicks.
With intuitive navigation and features, JuicePass is an app that makes charging your EV easier.
Enel X Way's mobile app works on all smartphone devices and in all countries allowing you to find the closest charging station when you travel.
JuicePass is convenient
With a few clicks JuicePass allows you to find where you can charge your EV, choose the rate plans that best suit your needs and customize your charging experience by entering your car make model.
JuicePass is multifunctional
Pick the charging station that works for your electric or hybrid car, find charging cost or availability hours and even reserve the charging station in advance.
Check your charging history, energy consumption, past invoices and more.
With JuicePass you can manage your home charging.
Configure and manage a JuiceBox home charger for a complete charging experience.
JuicePass allows you to:
Configure one or more JuiceBox chargers directly from the mobile app
Start or stop charging sessions or monitor charging progress.
Use smart charging features, postpone or delay charging start time and set its duration
Share your JuiceBox with other users
Download the app and start your journey into the world of electric mobility!
Follow us on Facebook at: https://www.facebook.com/enelxway
Need help? Write us at enelxway.italy.support@enel.com
